    { kind psi; a Ca; b Mg; c Cl; psi -0.012; source "Harvie, Moller & Weare, Geochim. Cosmochim. Acta 48 (1984) 723 (HMW seawater system); via USGS PHREEQC pitzer.dat (public domain)"; }
